{"tid":1886072,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實呢兩年係咪英超水平差左","createTime":"2020-02-18T17:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T01:27:09.000Z","uid":214007,"like":13,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9a6f789cb8b4542fd1d32656b4db95e4770d009f","tid":1886072,"uid":214007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"利記而家英超lead咁多 <br />\n去到歐聯都可以輸拿玻利<br />\n而拿玻璃係意甲只係排第9<br />\n如果今晚馬體會搞得掂利記<br />\n就再一次証明英超水準每況愈下<br />\n而家好多勁球員選擇踢德甲意甲而唔再係英超<br />\n來緊呢兩年如果連曼城都無得玩咁英超真係利玩哂<br />\n咁樣對英超來講一定係一件壞事<br />\n點解英超咁多年都咁多人中意係因為頭幾位競爭大<br />\n今年都肯定係利拎冠軍其實已經無咩好睇<br />\n就好似德甲意甲法甲西甲咁年年都個一兩隊拎<br />\n變到成個聯賽可觀性好低"},{"pid":"ac23cbd26b2fb6549aa4a3e697cafa970434ce90","tid":1886072,"uid":5649,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:10:57.000Z","msg":"係，差到歐聯決賽兩隊都係英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0406e946dcf93205c8bb100d8a53a7564dc58799","tid":1886072,"uid":47268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ac23cbd26b2fb6549aa4a3e697cafa970434ce90","tid":1886072,"uid":5649,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:10:57.000Z","msg":"係，差到歐聯決賽兩隊都係英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c43e33bf692734f89fe48bba2d53b35b59dd3fd","tid":1886072,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac23cbd26b2fb6549aa4a3e697cafa970434ce90","tid":1886072,"uid":5649,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:10:57.000Z","msg":"係，差到歐聯決賽兩隊都係英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97188b457dc48257120079f13bf4679ac22039eb","tid":1886072,"ui